    <item>
      <title>特朗普政策抑制商业投资的不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/uncertainty-about-trump-policies-set-to-curb-business-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普明年 1 月上任后将实施的经济政策存在不确定性，美国制造商的资本支出不会像许多人预期的那样在大选后出现增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/uncertainty-about-trump-policies-set-to-curb-business-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登免除近 43 亿美元公务员学生债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/student-loan-forgiveness-biden-cancels-about-4-3b-for-public-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登周五宣布，计划取消约 55,000 名公共部门工作人员的学生债务，他的政府将在其执政的最后几周内努力帮助更多人消除债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/student-loan-forgiveness-biden-cancels-about-4-3b-for-public-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东南亚国家誓言加大解决缅甸危机的力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/southeast-asian-nations-vow-to-ramp-up-myanmar-crisis-efforts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东南亚各国外交部长表示，随着人们对军政权能否继续掌权的怀疑日益加深，他们需要找到更有力的方式来帮助解决饱受战争蹂躏的缅甸的危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/southeast-asian-nations-vow-to-ramp-up-myanmar-crisis-efforts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 09:54:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰首都遭俄罗斯导弹袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ukraine-s-capital-comes-under-renewed-russian-missile-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在克里姆林宫领导人弗拉基米尔·普京提出与美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普举行会谈的第二天，乌克兰首都近一个月来首次遭遇俄罗斯导弹袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ukraine-s-capital-comes-under-renewed-russian-missile-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 07:51:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本执政党同意减税计划 遭盟友反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/japan-s-ruling-parties-agree-tax-plan-as-potential-ally-objects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本执政党在未与主要反对党达成协议的情况下批准了未来一年的税收改革计划，这加大了首相石破茂领导的少数派政府陷入进一步政治僵局的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/japan-s-ruling-parties-agree-tax-plan-as-potential-ally-objects</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 07:22:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果欧盟不购买更多美国石油和天然气，特朗普威胁征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/trump-threatens-sanctions-if-eu-doesn-t-buy-more-us-oil-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普警告欧盟，如果欧盟成员国不购买更多美国石油和天然气，其出口将受到美国关税的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/trump-threatens-sanctions-if-eu-doesn-t-buy-more-us-oil-gas</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 06:34:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾抗议、立法者冲突考验赖清德的领导力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/taiwan-protests-lawmaker-clashes-show-test-to-lai-s-leadership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾朝野政党之间掀起新一轮政治角力，引发街头抗议和议员争斗，这加剧了人们对赖清德总统是否有能力治理全球最危险的地缘政治热点地区之一的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/taiwan-protests-lawmaker-clashes-show-test-to-lai-s-leadership</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 02:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默任命曼德尔森为英国驻特朗普华盛顿特使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/starmer-taps-trade-veteran-mandelson-as-uk-s-ambassador-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 将任命资深工党人物和贸易专家彼得·曼德尔森 (Peter Mandelson) 为英国驻美国大使，以避免英国受到唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 征收关税的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/starmer-taps-trade-veteran-mandelson-as-uk-s-ambassador-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 20:05:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰召见匈牙利特使，化解日益升级的庇护案争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/hungary-grants-asylum-to-a-polish-fugitive-opposition-lawmaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在波兰总理维克托·奥尔班领导的政府为一名逃亡的波兰反对派议员提供庇护后，波兰召见了匈牙利驻华沙大使。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/hungary-grants-asylum-to-a-polish-fugitive-opposition-lawmaker</guid>
